trans-unit.source: The SoapHeaderMapping class represents a SOAP header mapping.
trans-unit.target: SoapHeaderMapping이 클래스는 SOAP 헤더 매핑을 나타냅니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets a <xref:System.Boolean> value that indicates whether the SOAP header mapping is custom-defined.
trans-unit.target: 가져옵니다는 <xref:System.Boolean>SOAP 헤더 매핑 사용자 정의 되어 있는지 여부를 나타내는 값입니다.</xref:System.Boolean>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the SOAP header mapping is custom-defined; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>사용자 정의; 경우 SOAP 헤더 매핑 그렇지 않으면 <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets a <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderDirection"></xref> value that indicates the direction of the SOAP header mapping.
trans-unit.target: 가져옵니다는 <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderDirection"> </xref> SOAP 헤더 매핑의 방향을 나타내는 값입니다.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderDirection"></xref> value that indicates the direction of the SOAP header mapping.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderDirection"> </xref> SOAP 헤더 매핑의 방향을 나타내는 값입니다.
